<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <%- include("partials/header"); -%>
  <style>
    /* Import Google Fonts */
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap');
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600&display=swap');

body {
    font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
    background-color: #e8f1f2;
    color: #333;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

.about-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
}

.about-container:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

.about-container h1 {
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #2c3e50;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.about-text p, .website-details p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    color: #555;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
}

.about-text p:hover, .website-details p:hover {
    color: #2980b9;
}

.website-details h2 {
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.website-details p {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
}

.website-details strong {
    color: #2980b9;
}

header, footer {
    background-color: #2980b9;
    color: #ffffff;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1rem;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
}

header h1, footer p {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
}

header:hover, footer:hover {
    background-color: #1c638d;
}

header h1:hover, footer p:hover {
    color: #ffffff;
}

footer p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
}

  </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="about-container">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <div class="about-text">
            <p>Welcome to our note-making website! We are dedicated to providing you with a simple and efficient platform to jot down your thoughts, ideas, and important information.</p>
            <p>Our mission is to help you stay organized and never miss a beat. Whether you're a student, professional, or anyone who needs a reliable note-taking solution, we've got you covered.</p>
            <p>Feel free to explore our features and start creating notes that matter to you. We're here to make your note-taking experience smooth and enjoyable.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="website-details">
            <h2>Website Details</h2>
            <p><strong>Website Name:</strong> Note the Thoughts</p>
            <p><strong>Founded:</strong> 2023</p>
            <p><strong>Contact Email:</strong> amanchandra4617@gmail.com</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>



